    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302628</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>申し遅れました。わたし、
この里の忍びたちを率いる
頭領、藤林&lt;Suzu&gt;と申します</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I apologize once again for the inconveniences.
I am commander and chief of this ninja
village, Fujibayashi &lt;Suzu&gt;.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302628</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おふたりのことは、
&lt;Rody&gt;さんから聞きました</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I have heard your story
already from Lady &lt;Rody&gt;.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302704</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>忍び？　この里って……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ninja...Village?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302800</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Suzu&gt;って……
もしかして、時空戦士の……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Suzu&gt;... You're the Hero of Time, &lt;Suzu&gt;!?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302884</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>え……率いるって、
その歳で……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Y-You're a village chief
at your age...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302972</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ほらほら、
いっきに色々質問しない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Guys, guys. Don't drown
poor &lt;Suzu&gt; in questions!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>303060</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Rody&gt;さんは
なんでここにいるの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What are you doing
here, Miss &lt;Rody&gt;?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>303156</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>待てよ……オレら、
元の時代に戻れてなくね？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Wait a second...then we
didn't return to our era?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>303256</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>はい、落ち着いて！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Now, calm DOWN!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>303256</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>深呼吸～！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Deep breaths!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>303388</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>はい……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Now...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>303388</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Suzu&gt;ちゃん、もう一度、
事情を話してあげてちょうだい</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Suzu&gt;, could you please go
over the recent events?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>303604</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_013&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ、はい……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>R-Roger...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>303604</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_014&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>実は最近、
魔界の王プルートが
この世界に侵攻してきたのです</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>As of late, Lord of Daemonium Pluto
has mounted a world wide invasion.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>303604</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_015&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そのせいで、地上の半分が、
今、瘴気の中に沈んでいます</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>As a result, the above ground has
been rended in half, releasing a
gas known as miasma.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>303696</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_016&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>じゃあ、みんな瘴気に
飲まれたのか！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Then...he wants everyone to
get enveloped in a miasma!?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>303804</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_017&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>避難した方もいますが、
瘴気に飲まれてしまった方も
います</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We've taken measures to
shelter the people. However,
the miasma is all-consuming.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>303916</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_018&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それとわたしたちが
捕まったことって
何か関係あるんですか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I assume us getting caught in this
mess isn't a coincidence, is it?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>304104</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_019&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>我々はその魔界の軍団と
戦っています</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We must battle against
the armies of Daemonium.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>304104</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_020&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>プルートの居場所がわからず、
その部下から話を聞くため、
生け捕りにしようかと……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>To do so, it's vital we learn of Pluto's whereabouts.
With that in mind, we are trying to capture one of
the minions alive for interrogation.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>304220</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_021&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>え……それってもしかして、
わたしたちを魔族と間違えた、
とか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Erhm... Are you telling us you
mistook us for Demons?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>21</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>304348</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_022&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……すみません。
人気のない場所に子どもふたりで
いらしたので怪しく思い……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...I sincerly apologize. It seemed rather
odd for a pair of normal children to
be in such a desolate, lifeless place.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>22</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>304516</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_024&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>本当にすみません……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I can't apologize enough for the offense...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>23</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>304628</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_025&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>頭領、アーリィが
再び闇に閉ざされたとの
報告が……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Chief. We've received reports that
the town of Arlee has been
covered in darkness once again...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>24</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>304720</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_026&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ダオスが現れた時と
同じ現象ですね……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Such a phenomenon occurred back
when we were at war with Dhaos...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>25</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>304840</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_027&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>プルートと何か関係がある
かもしれません。
調査に向かいます</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We do not know how this is related
to Pluto yet. Investigation is underway.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>26</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>304908</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_028&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>まかせました……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We are counting on your efforts...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>27</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305012</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_029&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>エトとも&lt;Couleur&gt;とも
はなればなれに
なっちゃったし……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Seems like we've gotten separated
from Eto and &lt;Couleur&gt;...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>28</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305088</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_030&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Couleur&gt;？
それって……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Couleur&gt;? Could that be...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>29</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305152</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_031&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クルール！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kuruuuru!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>30</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305232</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_032&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>うぉっと……！
おまえ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Whoa! Hey, you...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>31</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305308</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_033&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クルール！　クルール！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kuruuru! Kuruuuru! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>32</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305440</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_034&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おまえ、体があったかい……！
まさか……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Your body's all warm and
fuzzy... You didn't...!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>33</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305440</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_035&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……風呂入ってたな！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...You took a bath!?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>33</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305504</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_036&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クルクル♪</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kuru, kuru♪</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>35</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305584</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_037&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それじゃあ、
エトも一緒に？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Then Eto is here too?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>36</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305664</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_038&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いえ……
その子の他には誰も</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>No... There was no
one else besides him...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>37</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305808</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_040&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>どこ行っちゃったんだろう……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Where could she have gone...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>38</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305952</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_041&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>重ね重ねお詫び申し上げます</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Please accept my deepest apologies
for this embarrassing situation...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>39</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>305952</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_042&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>我が一族が
お力を貸せれば
よいのでしょうが……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>My scouts will lend you their support
to atone for this at once...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>39</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>306100</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_043&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>わかってます</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I completely understand...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>41</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>306100</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_044&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Suzu&gt;さんの一族は、
魔界の勢力と戦わなきゃ
いけないんですよね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But, right now your people
are too busy trying to fight
the Daemonium invasion.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>41</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>306196</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_045&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いえ……
せめて私だけでも
あなたたちの助けに</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's not a problem... At the
very least, I will personally help
to find your dear friend.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>43</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>306300</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_046&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、&lt;Suzu&gt;さんは頭領なんですよね？
……いいの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But &lt;Suzu&gt;, aren't you the chief? Is
it...okay to just help us like this?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>44</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>306388</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_047&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>失態の責任は
頭領である私が取ります</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That is why it is all the more
important. It is the duty of a
chief to redeem herself. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>45</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>306524</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_190_030_048&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>よし、んじゃ、決まり</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Okay fellas, then our next journey is decided!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
